{"id":15,"date":"2014-05-27T12:13:07","date_gmt":"2014-05-27T12:13:07","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/community\/ld4lt\/?p=15"},"modified":"2014-05-27T12:13:36","modified_gmt":"2014-05-27T12:13:36","slug":"roadmapping-linked-data-in-the-localisation-industry-dublin-4th-june14","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.w3.org\/community\/ld4lt\/2014\/05\/27\/roadmapping-linked-data-in-the-localisation-industry-dublin-4th-june14\/","title":{"rendered":"Roadmapping Linked Data in the Localisation Industry Dublin 4th June&#8217;14"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Following successful road-mapping workshops at the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.w3.org\/community\/ld4lt\/wiki\/LD4LT_Group_Kick-Off_and_Roadmap_Meeting\">European Data Forum<\/a> and the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.w3.org\/community\/ld4lt\/wiki\/LD4LT_Group_Madrid_May_2014_Meeting\">Multilingual Web conference<\/a>, the LD4LT group will next be engaging with the Localisation Industry on the 4th June&#8217;14 in Dublin, Ireland. This will be part of the <a href=\"http:\/\/www.localizationworld.com\/lwdub2014\/feisgiltt\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">FEISGILTT workshop<\/a> on harmonising localisation industry standards, which is co-located in <a href=\"http:\/\/www.localizationworld.com\/lwdub2014\/about.php\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Localisation World<\/a>, the industry&#8217;s premiere trade show. The focus will be on use cases where linked data can contribute to interoperability for localisation tools and processes, including terminology management and parallel text curation.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Following successful road-mapping workshops at the European Data Forum and the Multilingual Web conference, the LD4LT group will next be engaging with the Localisation Industry on the 4th June&#8217;14 in Dublin, Ireland. This will be part of the FEISGILTT workshop &hellip; <a href=\"https:\/\/www.w3.org\/community\/ld4lt\/2014\/05\/27\/roadmapping-linked-